# Layout

This view allows you to generate quickly and efficiently fully responsive layout (section).

## Features

{% set details = {
    layout: {
        title: 'Layout',
        description: 'The layout you want like `1 2 _ 3 3` with responsive capabilities'
    }
} %}

-   Generate fully responsive layouts
-   Easy and nice layout string notation like `1 1 2 _ 1 1 3`
-   Full support for medias specified in your `frontspec.json` file
{{ markdownSpecsList(props(specs.props), details) }}

## Usage

#### Blade

```php
@include('sugar.bare.layout.layout', [
    'id' => 'my-cool-layout',
    'layout' => [
        'desktop' => '1 1 2 _ 1 1 3'
        'mobile' => '1 _ 2 _ 3'
    ],
    'html' => '
        <div>Cell #1</div>
        <div>Cell #2</div>
        <div>Cell #3</div>
    ',
    'margin' => [
        'default' => [
            'bottom' => '50'
        ],
        'mobile' => [
            'bottom' => '20'
        ]
    ]
])
```

#### Twig

```twig
{{ '{%' }} include 'sugar.bare.layout.layout' with {
    layout: {
        desktop: '1 1 2 _ 1 1 3'
        mobile: '1 _ 2 _ 3'
    },
    html: '
        <div>Cell #1</div>
        <div>Cell #2</div>
        <div>Cell #3</div>
    ',
    margin: {
        default: {
            bottom: '50'
        },
        mobile: {
            bottom: '20'
        }
    }
} {{ '%}' }}
```

